"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1934673-Team-GB-Neah-Evans-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GBcyclist Neah Evans narrowly avoided a huge collision after falling off her bike during the women's omnium scratch race at theOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neah Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 34-year-old was nearly hit at speed by another cyclist on the last lap after losing her balance and tumbling down the banked final turn.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans was battling for position as the racers whizzed around the velodrome but found herself going for a gap that was not really there.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999989286152, \"rank\": 1.071431360295137e-09, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She ended up clipping the wheels of another rider, which sent her flying off her bike and forced the cyclist behind her to take evasive action.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit ended up flat on her back and took a few moments to compose herself before gingerly climbing back to her feet.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She eventually got back on her bike to cross the finish line in last place when the race had long since finished.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris Boardman, who won gold for Team GB in the individual pursuit in 1992, said on theBBC: \\\"It was just the overlapping wheel.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Boardman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Boardman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Boardman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Boardman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neah Evans just tried to go for a gap that simply wasn't there.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neah Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps a little bit of frustration.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She pushed into a gap and just had a bit of an overwheel.\\\"\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The frightening incident came two days after Evans helped Team GB to clinch silver in the women's madison alongside team-mate Elinor Barker.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999989286152, \"rank\": 1.071431360295137e-09, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.7768976362678697, \"rank\": 0.28717085260284153, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elinor_Barker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elinor Barker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elinor_Barker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elinor_Barker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did well to even make it to the Olympics, having recently struggled with a bacterial infection which left her unable to climb stairs.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on how the infection threatened to derail her Olympic hopes, Evans told theTeam GB website: \\\"The past 18 months have been really bad for me, if I am honest.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999989286152, \"rank\": 1.071431360295137e-09, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been several times when I have sat there and thought I am not going to make it.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Olympic swimmer fuming after 'vomiting nine times and suffering from diarrhoea'  Do not miss:Gender row boxer Lin Yu-ting wins Olympic gold and follows Imane Khelif's lead  Do not miss:Ollie Wood breaks silence after Team GB cyclist 'headbutted' by Dutch rival  \\\"The bacterial infection, it totally floored me.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.7768976362678697, \"rank\": 0.28717085260284153, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.5849772623658621, \"rank\": 0.3906674273705843, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My plan went out of the window and I just tried to get over that and see what I could do.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, at that point if you said I would go to an Olympics and win a silver medal, I would have said no chance.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"There were times when I was walking up the stairs, and halfway up I thought: 'I can not get up there'.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As an athlete, you downplay these things but this was almost quite scary.\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With injuries, you can not rush them but you can get around it, whereas with this I just had to recover.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am delighted to come away with silver and we had a really great battle.\\\"\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2904, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6738490373633502e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2953, \"end\": 2966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6738490373633502e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"